						<div class="postbody">I use Debian sid and choose to do almost everything the &quot;hard&quot; way (i.e. no desktop environment, and <em>especially</em> trying to avoid any GNOME components whenever possible).<br /><br />AFAICT, the biggest experience difference will be from your choice of desktop manager (KDE / GNOME / XFCE / LXDE / &amp;c)</div>

