			</td>
			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I run NixOS in a VM as my main development environment. The host (either Windows or macOS depending on which computer) is my real &quot;desktop&quot;; the VM just runs a very lightweight setup with xterm, xmonad, and non-X emacs. Nix is a dream to maintain but I can't speak as to how well full desktop environments or native hardware are supported on it. Still, I'd recommend giving it a shot.</div>

